summary: things i want from avengers: endgame
body:
things i want from avengers: endgame

  • Steve and Clint acting like their comics versions, because the MCU did them so dirty
  • Carol being badass and not being overshadowed by anyone
  • Carol and Thor being F R I E N D S, nothing more
  • Valkyrie being bisexual (for the ones who might argue this doesn’t belong in the movie, put it in an after credits scene or a small happy flirty comment to a girl -cough cough Carol- after they win)
  • Steve’s acknowledgement of his wrongdoings
  • Okoye being badass and having a significant role in all this madness
  • Tony and Rhodey and Pepper seeing each other for the first time in so long and being cute and caring about each other
  • Nebula getting a reunion with her sister
  • Same goes for Peter and Tony
  • And basically everyone who died and everyone who lost someone
  • Very few scenes with Wanda
  • Actual good happy moment between Thor and Loki when they recognise they’ve been fighting for so long and they’re ready to be decent to each other (basically maintaining the dynamic they had in taika’s masterpiece)
  • Pepper being the motherfucking queen of the MCU like she is, keeping everyone in line, scolding everyone when they mess up, and just generally being badass
  • WOMEN BEING AWESOME JUST BECAUSE WE ARE
  • More Bruce x Thor interactions because they are now close and all cute with each other
  • Tony playfully teasing Bruce after the war is over (could be over his crush on Thor, that would be very much acceptable)

summary: Captain Carol Danvers Captain Marvel Air Force Uniform Custom Funko Carol in her dress uniform with comic hair.  I did a version...
caption:
Captain Carol Danvers Captain Marvel Air Force Uniform Custom Funko

Carol in her dress uniform with comic hair.  I did a version with the longer mcu hair as well.  I do want to point out that having looked through lots of pictures of Carol in uniform no one drawing that comic seems to have ever bothered to look up what a woman’s air force uniform looks like.  Her body is Selina Meyers from Veep and her head is from the comic style Captain Marvel though I did paint her hair a brighter yellow (and contrasted that with the more “realistic” style for the mcu.

I will take commissions to replicate this funko, please contact privately to discuss price as the market for the figures in which I make these out of can change wildly.  Ask me about my etsy shop.

summary: Have you seen Captain Marvel? Thoughts?
question: Have you seen Captain Marvel? Thoughts?
answer:
Yesssss

I loved it. It was a necessary film, in my opinion, for the world to see right now.

I called most of what happened in it but I still enjoyed it nonetheless. I smiled the entire drive home and my roommate kept calling me a weirdo.

My fav moment probably had to be when she landed in the Blockbuster Video and everyone in the theater (who had ever actually been into a Blockbuster Video) laughed so hard. Then when she was talking about needing to find some communication equipment, I leaned over to Jacob and said “there has to be a Radio Shack close by, this is the 90’s after all” …. then the next shot it of a Radio Shack down the street and I died laughing.

I also love that Fury lost his eye to the flarken.


ALSO…. Coulson…. I Have Missed Him So Much


And don’t even get me started on Little Miss Carol “I’m such a lesbian in my Nine Inch Nails T-shirt and my leather jacket while I’m talking to my wife, Maria about our daughter” Danvers

(Thanks for the ask, friend 💜)
